-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Dataset license (separate from the materials above)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The microbiome dataset in data/ is the HITChip Atlas from:

  Lahti L, Salojarvi J, Salonen A, Scheffer M, de Vos WM (2014).
  Tipping elements in the human intestinal ecosystem.
  Nature Communications 5:4344. https://doi.org/10.1038/ncomms5344
  Data: Dryad, https://doi.org/10.5061/dryad.pk75d

It is released under the Creative Commons Zero (CC0 1.0) public-domain
dedication, which permits redistribution. Please cite the paper above when you
use the data. See data/SOURCE.md for details.

